title: APC NetShelter PDU: Outlet Status
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/power/apc
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the outlet status of APC NetShelter Advanced Rack PDU
 units (APDU series, OID subtree .318.1.1.32).

 It reports {OK} when the outlet is on and {WARN} when it is off.

item:
 The outlet index

discovery:
 One service is created for each outlet that is in state "on" at discovery time
